// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-1096 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 63010ed2-64de-58b6-b575-53566e5db011

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:16.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:16.10*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:17.04*")
